text: The Fiat Duna is an automobile made by Fiat between 1987 and 2000. It is a sedan and station wagon version of the Fiat Uno. == Engines == * 60 43 kW (58 hp) * 70 49 kW (67 hp) * DS 44 kW (60 hp) Duna Category:Front wheel drive vehicles Category:1980s automobiles Category:1990s automobiles Category:2000s automobiles
